title 0.4 new note

Browser->Server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note

note over Server: server responds with redirect and asks browser to do new GET request

Browser->Server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/notes
Server->Browser: HTML code
Browser->Server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.css
Server->Browser: CSS
Browser->Server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.js
Server->Browser:Javascript

note over Browser: Browser executes javascript and makes GET request to Server for JSON

Browser->Server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/data.json
Server->Browser: JSON

note over Browser: Browser continues to execute javascript file and appends note list to DOM
